message.body: So Julie's idiot Boyfriend won't take the cat now. You know anyone that would like a cat? He's the best!
If not do you know any places down there where I could take him to get adopted? I feel like there would be better than here
Oh noooo. Oh that's terrible. You should do a FB post because I bet there is someone. The best place here doesn't take kitties from the public, only from local shelters
It's called PAWs philly
Yeah that's what I figured. Good idea though
They do foster care though
If you put it on FB I will share it.
I out a thing on FB
Do you think Tessa would be interested? Though I know she has a million animals already
I don't think so with all the doggies but she might know someone.
Cool
I just shared it and will let you know if anyone gets a hold of me.
Awesome. Thanks! He's going Somewhere this weekend one way or another!
Can you text me a photo my sister might know someone
Ohhhh. He's so cute.
I know. Kills me.
Leah's gonna ask around at work
Awesome!!! Thank you!!!
I hope Malias friend takes him! Malia is a so nice and sweet and responsible I imagine her friends are too!
Who is malia?
She's on Facebook asking about him.
Ah! Just looked! Wrote her back. Awesome!!!
Do you have malia's number by chance?
Just want to text her. Need to get a home on lockdown
I don't :( I will try to procure it tho.
You so helpful
You guys are scheduled in at 12 yes? I have to go get my passport stuff in at 11. Hoping it won't take too long to get the paperwork in.
Yeah but no worries. We can chill in the park
Okay great. I'll have my phone ins
On
Awesome! It would be great if malia finds him a place so wouldn't have to drive him To Va
Yeah it would be really cool. I'm not having luck so far for her #.
She works a lot she might get back to you after 5
Cool. Thanks
